1
00:00:58,016 --> 00:01:00,992
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:00,992 --> 00:01:02,962
=Episode 14=

3
00:01:03,802 --> 00:01:06,938
(I'll Compensate You)

4
00:01:07,130 --> 00:01:11,514
(East City Gate)

5
00:01:15,480 --> 00:01:17,120
Isn't this Mr. Gu?

6
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:24,760
Perfect. It saves me the trouble
of going to your place.

7
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:27,599
Please give this to your wife.

8
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:33,079
And this too.

9
00:01:42,719 --> 00:01:45,359
Thank you, Mr. Gu. I'll take my leave.

10
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,120
Where is he?

11
00:02:11,599 --> 00:02:13,439
He said the weather's been cold lately.

12
00:02:13,639 --> 00:02:15,800
He was worried you might
feel unwell after drinking,

13
00:02:16,039 --> 00:02:17,719
so he prepared
some hot soup and went out.

14
00:02:18,719 --> 00:02:20,960
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)
Where did he go? Why not follow him?

15
00:02:21,599 --> 00:02:23,719
He went to the rouge shop.
A shadow guard's following.

16
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,400
What soup did he make?

17
00:02:53,199 --> 00:02:55,159
Something for the chill
and the wine, he said.

18
00:02:55,479 --> 00:02:56,680
Should I bring it now?

19
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:01,159
There's no need.
I'll wait for him to return.

20
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:19,479
Master, he said the soup
needs to be eaten warm.

21
00:03:23,159 --> 00:03:23,919
You may leave.

22
00:03:26,586 --> 00:03:28,776
笙ｪCarving a monument of longing笙ｪ

23
00:03:29,216 --> 00:03:31,040
笙ｪFor someone笙ｪ

24
00:03:31,258 --> 00:03:35,648
笙ｪI know the past can never be relived笙ｪ

25
00:03:36,608 --> 00:03:38,944
笙ｪLife after life笙ｪ

26
00:03:38,944 --> 00:03:41,792
笙ｪCannot discern right from wrong笙ｪ

27
00:03:42,675 --> 00:03:46,330
笙ｪI've failed you笙ｪ

28
00:03:47,930 --> 00:03:49,792
笙ｪPour this worldly brew笙ｪ

29
00:03:50,618 --> 00:03:52,448
笙ｪI raise my cup笙ｪ

30
00:03:52,448 --> 00:03:56,884
笙ｪAccompany you through ups and downs笙ｪ

31
00:03:58,010 --> 00:04:00,154
笙ｪTears of romance笙ｪ

32
00:04:00,544 --> 00:04:03,725
笙ｪYou smile so sadly笙ｪ

33
00:04:03,950 --> 00:04:06,599
笙ｪIt tears me apart inside笙ｪ

34
00:04:06,599 --> 00:04:08,439
Just go. Don't worry about me.

35
00:04:12,199 --> 00:04:13,719
How could I leave you behind?

36
00:04:13,719 --> 00:04:16,224
笙ｪLaugh at the gods笙ｪ

37
00:04:16,224 --> 00:04:18,094
笙ｪI have no regrets笙ｪ

38
00:04:18,842 --> 00:04:21,024
笙ｪThis sorrow笙ｪ

39
00:04:21,274 --> 00:04:23,763
笙ｪEndless tears笙ｪ

40
00:04:24,154 --> 00:04:26,630
笙ｪDrunk for you笙ｪ

41
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,839
A man, no matter how gentle his nature,

42
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:36,160
should protect his own wife.

43
00:04:40,442 --> 00:04:42,912
笙ｪMoonlight spills on duckweed笙ｪ

44
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:45,199
Don't worry. I'll be right back.

45
00:04:46,586 --> 00:04:49,440
笙ｪStill you enter my dreams笙ｪ

46
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:51,098
(Capital Yamen)

47
00:04:51,098 --> 00:04:53,952
笙ｪWatching the rain fall笙ｪ

48
00:04:53,952 --> 00:04:56,480
笙ｪReturning geese gaze at the pavilion笙ｪ

49
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:58,976
笙ｪThe tears welling in your eyes笙ｪ

50
00:04:58,976 --> 00:05:01,591
笙ｪFor whom do they fall笙ｪ

51
00:05:01,850 --> 00:05:04,544
笙ｪCan't escape parting in this lifetime笙ｪ

52
00:05:04,634 --> 00:05:07,269
笙ｪMeet again in the next life笙ｪ

53
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:08,279
You're back.

54
00:05:09,466 --> 00:05:10,048
Yeah.

55
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:35,800
Thank you.

56
00:05:45,639 --> 00:05:46,439
Go to sleep early.

57
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:46,360
How many days have we been guarding?

58
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:47,300
Who's there?

59
00:06:56,576 --> 00:06:57,216
Oh no!

60
00:07:05,879 --> 00:07:07,639
Did you hear that last night,

61
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:09,759
the unclaimed corpse
was stolen from the yamen?

62
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:13,160
Who would steal a corpse at night?

63
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,720
Yeah.

64
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:24,800
Wait, honey.

65
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:37,000
What is it?

66
00:07:39,279 --> 00:07:42,879
The corpse was already suspicious.

67
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,639
And now, it's stolen.

68
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:48,160
Who do you think could have done this?

69
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,519
I don't know.

70
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:54,879
The collapse of the Yunya Temple
has affected the surrounding people.

71
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:57,560
I've looked over Zhaoxi's account book.

72
00:07:58,199 --> 00:08:00,680
He used to provide
free consultations and donations.

73
00:08:02,319 --> 00:08:05,600
I plan to donate a batch
of supplies in his name.

74
00:08:07,639 --> 00:08:09,920
Since you've decided, just go ahead.

75
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:12,519
Honey.

76
00:08:16,458 --> 00:08:21,386
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)

77
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:26,879
Recently, there have been rumors saying
the corpse from the yamen is Zhaoxi.

78
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:31,279
So I hope you can join me
in confronting this.

79
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:37,320
But you needn't worry.
His past donations were anonymous.

80
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:40,799
You just need to check inside the hall

81
00:08:41,639 --> 00:08:44,000
and then wait quietly in the carriage.

82
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:02,559
Are you still feeling unwell today?

83
00:09:04,679 --> 00:09:05,480
No, I'm not.

84
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:13,720
The inventory has been completed.
You just need to go to the shop with me.

85
00:09:16,679 --> 00:09:20,320
I'm still feeling somewhat unwell.
Ask Xuan Qing to accompany you.

86
00:09:21,879 --> 00:09:24,279
She has already gone out
to do something for me.

87
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:28,919
You just said you were fine.

88
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:35,759
Though confined to home by illness,

89
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:38,759
Zhaoxi had anonymously
aided many people.

90
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:42,799
The pharmacy provides free consultations
and medicines monthly.

91
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,399
If he were still here today,

92
00:09:44,919 --> 00:09:49,039
upon hearing this matter,
he surely wouldn't ignore it.

93
00:09:52,159 --> 00:09:54,679
Master Zhaoxi is such a noble person.

94
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:58,240
No wonder you're willing to wade
into the muddy waters of the Gu family.

95
00:09:58,879 --> 00:10:00,120
It sounds like

96
00:10:04,879 --> 00:10:06,200
you're jealous.

97
00:10:09,759 --> 00:10:10,559
Of course not.

98
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:15,600
What happened that night

99
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,799
was caused by Spring Fever,

100
00:10:17,919 --> 00:10:20,480
but I'll do my best to compensate you.

101
00:10:23,844 --> 00:10:26,528
笙ｪMemories fade like the passing years笙ｪ

102
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:29,710
笙ｪThe past events leave us confused笙ｪ

103
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,120
How?

104
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:43,759
When Master Zhaoxi returns,
I'll apologize to him.

105
00:10:45,039 --> 00:10:47,960
Apologize? How exactly?

106
00:10:48,759 --> 00:10:50,200
By claiming we've been improper?

107
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:52,960
No, it was all on me.

108
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,519
You were drugged with Spring Fever.

109
00:10:57,279 --> 00:10:58,200
But I wasn't.

110
00:10:58,399 --> 00:11:02,200
If someone's to blame,
I should be the one to die for it.

111
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:04,399
We don't need to argue
about whose fault it was.

112
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:07,360
Let's just pretend this never happened.

113
00:11:10,894 --> 00:11:17,060
笙ｪAffection lingers, unforgettable笙ｪ

114
00:11:17,556 --> 00:11:22,112
笙ｪInk-stained scrolls recall bygones笙ｪ

115
00:11:22,112 --> 00:11:24,384
笙ｪEach stroke holds a thought笙ｪ

116
00:11:24,443 --> 00:11:30,624
笙ｪProsperity fades like dreams笙ｪ

117
00:11:31,584 --> 00:11:37,938
笙ｪWith nothing but memories left笙ｪ

118
00:11:43,370 --> 00:11:47,274
(Yunya Temple)

119
00:11:52,399 --> 00:11:53,399
Move this over there.

120
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,600
Sir.

121
00:12:04,399 --> 00:12:05,279
Thank you all.

122
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:12,600
Aren't we going to the temple?

123
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:16,240
I'll take you somewhere.

124
00:12:31,639 --> 00:12:32,799
Have some water.

125
00:12:32,799 --> 00:12:33,399
Thank you.

126
00:12:35,279 --> 00:12:36,320
Take the medicine on time.

127
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,840
Thank you.

128
00:12:43,679 --> 00:12:46,399
Son, let the physician examine you.

129
00:12:57,559 --> 00:12:59,919
The heavy rain days ago
caused the temple's collapse.

130
00:13:00,919 --> 00:13:04,559
Many merchants donated
to the temple at Prince Rui's call.

131
00:13:05,399 --> 00:13:08,799
But few people know
the rain also brought disaster

132
00:13:08,919 --> 00:13:09,799
upon these hunters.

133
00:13:10,639 --> 00:13:14,919
Fearing they'd be forgotten, I asked
a physician to offer free treatment.

134
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:16,519
But I didn't expect

135
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:20,559
Chaosheng had already sent
supplies ahead of time.

136
00:13:26,879 --> 00:13:30,320
Something's come up at home.
Please enjoy yourselves.

137
00:13:40,399 --> 00:13:41,200
What's wrong?

138
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:46,120
I was just wondering
what kind of person Chaosheng truly is.

139
00:13:47,559 --> 00:13:49,080
Everyone has both good and evil sides.

140
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:51,840
Everyone wants to play the saint
when they're on top.

141
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:54,759
But when they're down and out,
how can we mock their wickedness?

142
00:13:56,399 --> 00:14:00,240
Rather than judging others,
why not leave them a path to goodness?

143
00:14:01,519 --> 00:14:04,360
So this was the message
you received before leaving?

144
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:09,799
Now that they have help and a physician,

145
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:12,480
they likely need no further assistance.

146
00:14:12,919 --> 00:14:13,879
Let's head back now.

147
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:19,279
They're back!

148
00:14:19,279 --> 00:14:20,000
Come on!

149
00:14:20,679 --> 00:14:21,320
How did it go?

150
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:24,759
Let me catch my breath. Listen.

151
00:14:25,279 --> 00:14:28,480
Those officials claimed
our collapsed houses were our own fault.

152
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,320
They won't help.

153
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:33,039
I just knew it before we went.

154
00:14:33,279 --> 00:14:35,200
Thankfully, Mr. Gu Chaosheng
and Mr. Gu Zhaoxi

155
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,440
sent us all this food.

156
00:14:36,440 --> 00:14:37,919
Yes. All thanks to the Gu family.

157
00:14:37,919 --> 00:14:39,240
They are so kind.

158
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:48,879
One more thing.
Wasn't the temple's wall washed away?

159
00:14:49,279 --> 00:14:50,840
Today, when repairing it,

160
00:14:50,879 --> 00:14:53,240
the workers found
a corpse in the collapsed corner.

161
00:14:53,399 --> 00:14:54,679
- A corpse?
- A corpse?

162
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,639
How could a corpse appear there?

163
00:14:56,759 --> 00:14:57,840
Who knows?

164
00:14:59,679 --> 00:15:01,120
Didn't you already help them?

165
00:15:01,399 --> 00:15:03,360
Why do you still look so troubled?

166
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:06,720
I never like
meddling in others' affairs.

167
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:09,759
But if Zhaoxi saw this,

168
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:14,120
his kind heart
would bring him much distress.

169
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:18,840
If he returns safely,
you two could save the people.

170
00:15:22,679 --> 00:15:25,200
How could mere merchants
like us save the people?

171
00:15:27,519 --> 00:15:31,080
But I've heard
Prince Rui seems troubled lately.

172
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:35,440
With the Crown Prince gone,
if he truly wishes to serve the people,

173
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:39,039
it might actually be a blessing.

174
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:43,159
You think so too?

175
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:48,919
I'm merely a woman.

176
00:15:51,720 --> 00:15:53,840
What does being a merchant
or a woman matter?

177
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:57,279
A heart for the people
is like a drop of water.

178
00:15:57,600 --> 00:15:59,639
It could become
the first rain in a drought

179
00:16:00,120 --> 00:16:02,200
or the last drop for the dying.

180
00:16:03,639 --> 00:16:04,440
Master.

181
00:16:05,519 --> 00:16:08,360
Master, a corpse was discovered
beneath the Yunya Temple's wall.

182
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:10,200
It belongs to a grown man.

183
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,360
Officials have taken it away.

184
00:16:12,679 --> 00:16:14,519
He carried physicians' needles
and medicines.

185
00:16:15,039 --> 00:16:18,480
Officers found an incense pouch on him
that clashed with his simple clothing.

186
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:22,279
But I think it looks like
Master Chaosheng's.

187
00:16:24,720 --> 00:16:25,399
You may leave.

188
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:26,340
Yes.

189
00:16:43,399 --> 00:16:45,480
If the corpse was buried long ago
beneath that wall,

190
00:16:45,879 --> 00:16:48,360
it should've been found
when the rain collapsed it.

191
00:16:49,039 --> 00:16:50,000
Are you suggesting

192
00:16:50,279 --> 00:16:53,080
that the corpse was placed there
after the collapse?

193
00:16:57,639 --> 00:17:00,000
Do you think he killed that person?

194
00:17:05,079 --> 00:17:07,000
Gu Chaosheng is at the temple right now.

195
00:17:07,359 --> 00:17:10,519
It's only a matter of time
before officials trace the pouch to him.

196
00:17:11,279 --> 00:17:15,240
Wouldn't ordinary people first wonder
about the corpse's identity?

197
00:17:16,279 --> 00:17:17,799
You haven't even seen the corpse.

198
00:17:18,599 --> 00:17:20,440
Why focus on the killer first?

199
00:17:21,640 --> 00:17:23,559
Because this involves Chaosheng.

200
00:17:26,359 --> 00:17:27,759
Aren't you curious at all

201
00:17:28,839 --> 00:17:29,920
about who the dead man is?

202
00:17:32,119 --> 00:17:35,119
Didn't Chaosheng bring
a physician to test my condition?

203
00:17:35,279 --> 00:17:36,160
Wasn't it him?

204
00:17:45,162 --> 00:17:48,810
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)

205
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:57,880
Don't overexert yourself.
You should rest sometimes.

206
00:18:05,920 --> 00:18:08,319
This month's batch
of new herbs has arrived.

207
00:18:08,799 --> 00:18:10,519
Xuan Qing is taking inventory today.

208
00:18:11,119 --> 00:18:14,960
I also told her to bring back
the herbs that are good for your body.

209
00:18:52,079 --> 00:18:54,400
Thank you.

210
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:58,799
There's no need to say that between us.

211
00:18:59,920 --> 00:19:01,480
For your health,

212
00:19:02,039 --> 00:19:03,920
I would brave ten thousand perils

213
00:19:04,319 --> 00:19:08,079
to find the legendary elixir.

214
00:19:13,319 --> 00:19:16,440
Don't you love slightly sour grapes?

215
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:19,079
Eat more if you want to.

216
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:53,359
Have you had enough fun?

217
00:19:54,400 --> 00:19:55,200
No.

218
00:20:12,480 --> 00:20:13,279
Master.

219
00:20:18,559 --> 00:20:19,480
Speak freely.

220
00:20:22,279 --> 00:20:25,519
As you instructed,
I've carefully examined that skeleton.

221
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:28,680
Based on the bone length and age,

222
00:20:29,440 --> 00:20:32,519
it is most likely Master Zhaoxi.

223
00:21:10,330 --> 00:21:15,393
笙ｪWillows sway in the twilight breeze笙ｪ

224
00:21:15,930 --> 00:21:21,251
笙ｪAncient alleys guard time's secrets笙ｪ

225
00:21:21,818 --> 00:21:28,446
笙ｪBluestones bear life's imprints笙ｪ

226
00:21:28,446 --> 00:21:33,210
笙ｪFalling petals, endless longing笙ｪ

227
00:21:33,210 --> 00:21:35,546
笙ｪLonging lingers within my heart笙ｪ

228
00:21:35,546 --> 00:21:42,246
笙ｪZither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting笙ｪ

229
00:21:42,246 --> 00:21:49,018
笙ｪPast tales nest in my soul笙ｪ

230
00:21:49,018 --> 00:21:56,154
笙ｪAffection lingers, unforgettable笙ｪ

231
00:21:56,154 --> 00:22:00,538
笙ｪInk-stained scrolls recall bygones笙ｪ

232
00:22:00,538 --> 00:22:03,162
笙ｪEach stroke holds a thought笙ｪ

233
00:22:03,162 --> 00:22:09,796
笙ｪProsperity fades like dreams笙ｪ

234
00:22:09,796 --> 00:22:16,346
笙ｪPast tales nest in my soul笙ｪ

235
00:22:16,346 --> 00:22:23,470
笙ｪAffection lingers, unforgettable笙ｪ

236
00:22:23,560 --> 00:22:27,930
笙ｪInk-stained scrolls recall bygones笙ｪ

237
00:22:27,930 --> 00:22:30,638
笙ｪEach stroke holds a thought笙ｪ

238
00:22:30,638 --> 00:22:36,538
笙ｪProsperity fades like dreams笙ｪ

239
00:22:37,178 --> 00:22:43,166
笙ｪPast tales nest in my soul笙ｪ
